{
  "message": "test(masked): lock set_fill_value / filled edge-case parity\n\nAdded 7 golden fixtures exercising fill_value boundary conditions\nin the masked filled() path:\n\n- fully-masked 1-D: all elements replaced by fill\n- no-mask 1-D: fill has no effect (identity)\n- collision: fill_value equals existing data value\n- large fill: 1e300 across masked positions\n- zero fill on data containing real zeros (confirms mask, not\n  value, drives replacement)\n- 2-D checkerboard mask with negative fill\n- negative fill over positive data\n\n62 masked_differential cases total. Suite stays green.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
